des:
With the U-Smart-AI skill for Amazon Alexa, you can now easily control your connected thermostat by voice! Ask Alexa to turn the thermostat on/off, set the temperature, adjust the fan speed, and more. (This skill is specifically for the US region, there would be another for the EU region soon)
If you have any problems, please contact us at service@rti-tek.com.

Before using the skill, you need an account of our "U-Smart-AI" app first:
(1)Search and download our "U-Smart-AI" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2)Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you're already registered);
(3)Turn on your thermostats and connect them with "U-Smart-AI" app;

To get started, you need to follow the guide below step-by-step and enable the U-Smart-AI Alexa skill:
(1)Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(2)Search the Alexa Skills directory for "U-Smart-AI";
(3)Click to enable skill of "U-Smart-AI", then input your U-Smart-AI account username and password on the linking page;
(4)Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your thermostats.

Example phrases are:
"Alexa, turn off the thermostat."
"Alexa, set thermostat to 25 degrees."
"Alexa, set thermostat to automatic mode."
"Alexa, set thermostat to manual mode."
"Alexa, get thermostat temperature."
"Alexa, set living room fan speed to low."
"Alexa, set living room to cool mode."
